description.fr: Après les événements survenus dans les galeries de la faille d'{WorldZone:208[Astrub]}, {CharacterName:474}, {CharacterName:596} et {CharacterName:708} se réunissent pour organiser leurs actions.
description.en: After the events in the tunnels in the {WorldZone:208[Astrub]} rift, {CharacterName:474}, {CharacterName:596} and {CharacterName:708} are working together to coordinate their actions.
description.es: Tras los sucesos ocurridos en las galerías de la falla de {WorldZone:208[Astrub]}, {CharacterName:474}, {CharacterName:596} y {CharacterName:708} se reúnen para organizar sus acciones.
description.de: Nach den Ereignissen, die sich in den Tunneln des Risses in {WorldZone:208[Astrub]} zugetragen haben, kommen {CharacterName:474}, {CharacterName:596} und {CharacterName:708} wieder zusammen, um ihre Aktionen zu koordinieren.
description.pt: Depois dos eventos ocorridos nas galerias da fenda de {WorldZone:208[Astrub]}, {CharacterName:474}, {CharacterName:596} e {CharacterName:708} se reuniram para organizar suas ações.

descriptionFinished.fr: L'apparition de la Déesse dans les galeries ne laisse aucun doute à {CharacterName:474}\_: la Déesse est prisonnière des Shushus. Elle s'organise avec {CharacterName:596} et {CharacterName:708} pour la libérer.
descriptionFinished.en: The appearance of the goddess in the tunnels has made one thing clear\_– the goddess is being held prisoner by the Shushus. {CharacterName:474}'s coordinating with {CharacterName:596} and {CharacterName:708} to free her.
descriptionFinished.es: La aparición de la diosa en las galerías no le deja lugar a dudas a {CharacterName:474}: la diosa está prisionera de los fab'huritus. Esta se organiza con {CharacterName:596} y {CharacterName:708} para liberarla.
descriptionFinished.de: Dass die Göttin in den Tunneln aufgetaucht ist, kann für {CharacterName:474} nur eins bedeuten: Die Göttin wird von den Shushus gefangen gehalten! Gemeinsam mit {CharacterName:596} und {CharacterName:708} will sie sie retten.
descriptionFinished.pt: A aparição da Deusa nas galerias não deixa nenhuma dúvida a {CharacterName:474}: a Deusa é prisioneira dos Shushus. Ela está se organizando com {CharacterName:596} e {CharacterName:708} para libertá-la.
